        <abstract>
            <t>
                This document presents suggestions for the use of BPG Large Communities <xref target="RFC8092" /> at Internet Exchange Points (IXPs) based on operational experiences from IXP members this document suggests catergories of communities.
		Any IXP operator or IXP member can consider using these communities. The document specifically focusses on Route Server <xref target="RFC7947" /> deployments in IXP context <xref target="RFC7948" />.
            </t>
        </abstract>
